Subject: [PATCH 07/10] =?UTF-8?q?F-06/F-04/F-09=20+=20bugfixes:=20stockvel?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20=E2=80=94=20cash=20and=20liability=20finally=20move=20togeth?=
 =?UTF-8?q?er?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Contributions (including the initial contribution at registration)
  now RAISE capital; bonus and contribution payouts LOWER it, each with
  a capital-sufficiency guard; memberFundsHeld is recalculated after
  every mutation, so the dashboard's lendable figure
  (capital − member funds held) is finally honest. (F-06)
- The manual 'loan_payment' receipt fabricated a hardcoded 10% bonus
  ('Example' in the original comment) — removed; the real bonus rule
  runs in Active Loans makePayment. The receipt remains a record.
- payoutBonus zeroed a member's ENTIRE accrued bonus regardless of the
  amount actually paid — now subtracts only what was paid, with
  amount>0 / ≤accrued / ≤capital guards.
- renewMembership computed the new expiry via toISOString(), shifting
  SAST dates back a day — now uses the shared timezone-safe rule.
- Receipts, payouts, and registrations log to the canonical
  AppState.transactions. (F-09)
- Member names, phones, account numbers, and notes escaped in all
  eleven render templates; sanitize.js loaded; logs behind DEBUG.
  (F-04/F-17)

Transform preserved for audit: tools/transform-stockvel.mjs
